caption:
Checkerboard nails are having a MOMENT this spring! From bright colors to muted tones, we are seeing them EVERYWHERE! 

If you’re struggling with drawing them, don’t worry! We’ve got you! Here, @matythenailgal does a a quick and easy tutorial that will get you nailing this design in no time!! 

Love these on-trend spring colors? We’ve tagged them for easy check out! You’re welcome! 😉 #ericasata #springnailart #checkerboard #springnails
